ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectAGREEMENT - Bring into force St. Vincent and the Grenadines FOR THE EXCHANGE OF INFORMATION ON TAX MATTERS
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the actions necessary to bring into force for Canada the AGREEMENT between the Government of Canada and ST. VINCENT AND THE GRENADINES FOR THE EXCHANGE OF INFORMATION ON TAX MATTERS, signed in St. Vincent and the Grenadines on 22 June 2010.
